description: Try our easy to follow Honey Chicken Stir-Fry recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Honey Chicken Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Defrost bag with chicken in fridge overnight. Heat a wok over high heat. Add oil. Transfer chicken to wok, reserving marinade. Stir-fry in batches, tossing often, for 4-5 minutes or until golden. Add frozen vegetables and cook for 2-3 minutes or until tender. Add reserved marinade to wok. Cook for 2 minutes. Serve with steamed rice.
